The user requested the AI to change the text to a pirate-themed style, and the AI acknowledged this multiple times, stating, "Sure, I’m changing the text to be pirate themed now!" Following this, the user asked the AI to change an image to a Kamehameha, to which the AI responded positively, indicating it would proceed with the request. Additionally, the user was provided with a checklist of features to consider implementing, including a dynamic effects section and recent user selections display. The user was also asked questions regarding the size and placement of a Hadoken fireball image, with the AI again affirming it would make the necessary changes. Later, the user asked for an email form to be added for Santa, which the AI agreed to do, while offering another set of features for consideration, including error messages and an email input field. The user also requested an addition of a Hadoken button, with the AI confirming it would carry out this task as well. The AI then inquired for more details about the project.
